To build the package on Debian Wheezy:

    git clone https://github.com/flaf/shinken-package.git
    cd shinken-package/shinken
    tar --strip-components=1 -zxvf ../shinken_1.4.1.orig.tar.gz
    apt-get update
    apt-get install --no-install-recommends -y python quilt python-setuptools debhelper build-essential
    dpkg-buildpackage -us -uc


